[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1368","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1368.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1155","title":"LakeWeb Mail List CGI脚本远程命令执行漏洞","description":"LakeWeb Mail List CGI 脚本存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者可通过在收件人电子邮件地址中插入 shell 元字符（如管道符、分号等）执行任意系统命令。该漏洞源于程序未对用户输入的邮件地址进行充分过滤和转义，导致恶意命令被传递给底层 shell 执行。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用此漏洞，获取服务器控制权。受影响的 LakeWeb Mail List 版本需及时升级或采取输入验证措施。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1155"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-11-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:50.277","remediation":"在 LakeWeb Mail List CGI 脚本中对 recipient 邮件地址参数严格过滤 shell 元字符（; | & ` $ ( )），禁止包含 ! # $ & * + ? 等特殊字符的请求；升级到官方修补版本或改用参数化调用方式替代 system/popen 执行外部命令；如无法升级，建议将脚本迁移至 Python/Perl 的邮件库（如 smtplib）以彻底避免 shell 注入风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://lakeweb.com/scripts/","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/11175","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1400","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1155.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1155","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1155.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1155.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-39v6-whcc-chg3/GHSA-39v6-whcc-chg3.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88927/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1155.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000383.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--75ad1242-63af-4506-9559-c3c6161166d5.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1368.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1368.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1368.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1366","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1366.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1153","title":"HAMcards Postcard CGI 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"HAMcards Postcard CGI 脚本 1.0 存在操作系统命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向收件人邮箱地址参数中注入 shell 元字符执行任意系统命令，从而完全控制受影响服务器。该漏洞因程序未对用户输入进行有效过滤导致，任何部署了该 CGI 脚本的 Web 服务器均可能受到影响，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1153"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-11-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:50.030","remediation":"立即从 Web 服务器中删除或禁用 HAMcards Postcard CGI 脚本（postcard.cgi），该脚本已停止维护且存在 shell 元字符注入漏洞。替代方案：使用 PHP 或 Python 等现代语言重写明信片功能，对收件人邮箱地址做严格白名单过滤（仅允许字母、数字、@、.、-、_），并确保 CGI 进程以最低系统权限运行。如无法立即移除，可在 Apache/Nginx 中限制该脚本仅允许受信任 IP 访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/11175","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1400","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1153.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1153","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1153.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9b79b5eac5a874eeb91f0d9e37084feed8b830f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1153.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-673c-2gx6-44f7/GHSA-673c-2gx6-44f7.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88526/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1153.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/b82432e7d59d95db9f183c0cefa7744595784afa/1999.tsv","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000381.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1366.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1366.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1366.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1367","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1367.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1154","title":"LakeWeb Filemail CGI 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"LakeWeb Filemail CGI 脚本对用户输入的 recipient 电子邮件地址字段未做任何过滤，直接拼接传递给后端 shell 命令执行。攻击者可构造包含分号、管道符等 shell 元字符的恶意邮件地址，在服务器上以 Web 服务器权限执行任意系统命令，进而获取敏感信息、植入后门或控制整台服务器。该漏洞无需身份验证，攻击者仅需发送特制 HTTP 请求即可远程触发。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1154"],"sources":["cve","epss"],"published":"1998-11-09","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"立即联系厂商获取已修复版本，或在 CGI 脚本中对 recipient 邮箱字段做严格的输入过滤，移除 `;` `|` `&` `` ` `` `$` `()` `{}` `[]` 等 shell 元字符，并对 `@` `.` 等合法字符做白名单校验；建议使用 Perl 的 `quotemeta()` 函数或安全 API 替代直接拼接 shell 命令。如产品已停止维护，建议替换为持续更新维护的邮件发送方案或禁用该 CGI 脚本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://lakeweb.com/scripts/","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/11175","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1400"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1367.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1367.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1367.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1452","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1452.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1284","title":"Puppets Place NukeNabber 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"NukeNabber 存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向该软件的 1080 端口建立连接但不发送任何数据，触发 report.exe 程序执行并导致目标主机 CPU 占用率升至 100%，造成系统拒绝服务。该漏洞攻击条件简单，无需认证即可利用，影响范围包括 NukeNabber 相关版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1284"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-11-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:06.550","remediation":"NukeNabber 软件已停止维护且不再更新，建议立即卸载或停止使用该软件。如业务必须使用，可在防火墙层面限制仅允许可信 IP 访问 TCP 1080 端口，并配置入侵检测规则监控对该端口的异常空连接行为，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91063407332594&w=2","http://www.dynamsol.com/puppet/text/new.txt","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/11131","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1540","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1284.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1284","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1284.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1284.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-92rh-3xpw-hjgg/GHSA-92rh-3xpw-hjgg.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1284.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--bcd9f4b2-1177-414c-af67-66e5fcab77ab.json","https://github.com/io0323/vulnerability-lab/blob/3477460727500d821df1a577c343a03a904f7441/web/src/data/attacks.ts","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/be7ad03fdf3a412f0fd57a25f1732dc0ecfb1cb3/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1452.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0141","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0141.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0052","title":"FreeBSD/OpenBSD IP碎片重组空指针解引用拒绝服务漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 和 OpenBSD 操作系统在处理 IP 分片重组时存在空指针解引用漏洞 (CWE-476)。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统发送精心构造的异常 IP 分片数据包，当内核试图对这些分片进行重组时会因空指针解引用导致系统崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 FreeBSD 1.x/2.x、OpenBSD 2.2/2.3 及 BSD/OS 4.0 等多个版本，CVSS v3.1 评分 7.5，危害等级高。由于攻击无需任何特权且可远程触发，是早期 BSD 系统中影响广泛的拒绝服务漏洞之一。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0052"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-11-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:27.813","remediation":"建议升级 FreeBSD 至 2.2.8 及以上版本，或 OpenBSD 至 2.4 及以上版本；在防火墙层面丢弃入站分片数据包（如 iptables -A INPUT -f -j DROP），或在内核中禁用 IP 分片重组功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/908","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1389"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0141.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0439","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0439.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0254","title":"HP OpenView SNMP 团体字符串信息泄露漏洞","description":"HP OpenView 存在隐藏的 SNMP 团体字符串漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可利用该默认团体字符串访问 SNMP 服务，进而读取或修改 MIB 表中的敏感配置信息，导致信息泄露或设备配置被篡改。受影响的系统包括 HP OpenView 网络管理软件，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0254"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-11-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:00.633","remediation":"升级 HP OpenView 至 NNM 7.53 或更高版本以修复此已知漏洞；立即修改所有 SNMP 团体字符串，禁止使用默认的 public/private 及已知隐藏字符串；在防火墙上限制仅允许受信任的管理主机访问 UDP 161 端口；如业务不需要 SNMP 功能，建议直接禁用 OpenView 的 SNMP 代理服务以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0254","https://www.broadcom.com/support/fibre-channel-networking/security-advisories/brocade-security-advisory-2017-239","https://www.broadcom.com/support/fibre-channel-networking/security-advisories/brocade-security-advisory-2017-239/","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0254.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0254","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0254.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0254.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0254.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cve-reference-ingest-data/blob/c8b30957414aefbd6ba0b766db0d40593ba36fba/references/CVE-1999-0254-2025-03-17-1422","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p4hh-f88r-4p2r/GHSA-p4hh-f88r-4p2r.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cve-reference-ingest/blob/edcc863fa08f9024b1a3afc6f793747fed5f08ff/references/contrib1-CVE-1999-0254-2025-03-17-1422","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/snmp_default_communities.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0439.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0261","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0261.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0118","title":"IBM AIX 4.3 infod 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.3 系统的 infod 组件存在本地权限提升漏洞，本地攻击者可通过 X display 机制向 infod 服务发送特制请求，利用该漏洞获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 AIX 4.3 版本系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用，成功利用后完全控制系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0118"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-11-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:37.630","remediation":"建议升级到 IBM AIX 4.3.3 及以上受支持版本，或安装对应 APAR 补丁 IX72357。如无需 infod 服务，可执行 `stopsrc -t infod` 停止该服务并通过注释 `/etc/inetd.conf` 中相关行禁用，以消除攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91158980826979&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19287","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0118.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0118","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0118.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0118.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0118.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7pq8-h83c-wwjc/GHSA-7pq8-h83c-wwjc.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0118.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6c29fe92-c11f-40b7-bc14-92d730f9e4fc.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0261.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0402","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0402.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0215","title":"SGI IRIX 和 OpenLinux routed 守护进程文件追加漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 3/4/5/6 及 OpenLinux 1.0/1.1 系统中运行的 routed 路由守护进程存在文件追加写入漏洞。攻击者可通过向目标系统的 routed 服务发送特制的 traceon 路由跟踪数据包，将任意数据追加到系统文件末尾，包括 /etc/passwd 等关键文件，进而实现权限提升或系统控制。该漏洞利用无需认证，远程即可触发，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0215"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-10-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:55.790","remediation":"建议禁用 routed 服务并改用静态路由或 gated 替代。如确需运行，升级到 IRIX 6.5.2+ 或 OpenLinux 1.1.2+ 版本，并在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释 routed 条目后重启 inetd 服务以立即消除攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-012.shtml","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20805","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0215.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0215","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0215.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0215.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-45w3-m25h-r87g/GHSA-45w3-m25h-r87g.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0215.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--580f5a91-46c0-44d8-8dec-8f18301e9dd8.json","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0402.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0207","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0207.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0088","title":"IRIX 和 AIX automountd 服务远程代码执行漏洞","description":"IRIX 和 AIX 系统中的 automountd（autofsd）服务存在远程命令执行漏洞。攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统的该服务发送特制请求，利用服务对输入参数过滤不严的缺陷，以 root 权限执行任意命令，完全控制受影响主机。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，影响 IRIX 及 AIX 操作系统。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0088"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-10-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:33.370","remediation":"在 AIX 系统上执行 `stopsrc -g automountd` 禁用自动挂载服务，编辑 `/etc/rc.autofs` 注释自动启动项；在 IRIX 系统上执行 `/etc/init.d/autofs stop` 并删除 rc 链接。同时使用防火墙规则过滤 TCP/UDP 6969 端口，限制对 automountd 服务的网络访问。建议将老旧 IRIX/AIX 系统迁移至受支持版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www-1.ibm.com/services/brs/brspwhub.nsf/advisories/852567CC004F9038852566BF007B6393/%24file/ERS-SVA-E01-1998_004_1.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0207.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0143","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0143.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0053","title":"FreeBSD TCP RST 数据包拒绝服务漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 6.2 的 TCP 协议栈存在 TCP RST 包拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过伪造 TCP RST 数据包向已建立的 TCP 连接发送，导致目标系统上的合法 TCP 连接被异常中断。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，可造成受影响服务的可用性下降，影响范围包括运行 FreeBSD 6.2 的系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0053"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-10-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:28.047","remediation":"升级至 FreeBSD 7.0-RELEASE 或更高版本，该漏洞已在 FreeBSD 6.3-STABLE 分支的 tcp_input.c 补丁中修复。若无法升级，可在 pf 防火墙上添加规则限制每秒入站 RST 包数量：`pass in proto tcp flags R/R` 结合 `max-packets 100/sec` 作为临时缓解。同时建议在系统层面启用 syncookies（sysctl net.inet.tcp.syncookies=1）以降低 RST 欺骗影响。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6094"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0143.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0005","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0005.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0002","title":"Caldera OpenLinux NFS mountd 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NFS 服务中的 mountd 组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 请求触发该漏洞，成功利用后可获得 root 权限，实现完全控制目标系统。该漏洞主要影响 RedHat Linux 5.1、Caldera OpenLinux Standard 1.2 等 Linux 发行版，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0002"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-10-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:18.113","remediation":"立即升级 NFS mountd 相关软件包。Red Hat Linux 用户应升级至 5.2 及以上版本；Caldera OpenLinux 用户应升级至 Standard 1.3 及以上版本。临时缓解措施：在防火墙上封锁 NFS 相关端口（如 TCP/UDP 111、2049），或直接禁用 NFS 服务（`/etc/init.d/nfs stop`）及 rpc.mountd 守护进程。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-006.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/121","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19096"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0005.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0003","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0003.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0002","title":"Linux NFS mountd 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NFS mountd 组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 请求触发该漏洞，成功利用后可获取受影响系统的 root 权限。该漏洞主要影响 Linux 系统，包括 RedHat Linux 5.1 及 Caldera OpenLinux Standard 1.2 等版本。CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，建议立即升级至修复版本。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0002"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-10-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:18.113","remediation":"RedHat Linux 5.1 用户应升级至 RedHat Linux 5.2 或安装对应安全补丁；Caldera OpenLinux Standard 1.2 用户需更新至修复版本；SGI 系统应安装公告 19981006-01-I 提供的补丁。在不影响业务的前提下，可禁用 NFS 服务（/etc/init.d/nfs stop）或使用 tcpwrappers（/etc/hosts.allow）限制对 rpc.mountd 的访问来源，同时通过防火墙仅允许可信 IP 访问 RPC 端口（111/TCP/UDP）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-006.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/121","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19096","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0002.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0002.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0002","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/62aa382b460e7aee53e2fc9ebcfd565bebdac259/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0002.json","https://github.com/demisto/content/blob/710308a4be78e89bc993b4d594b444aeb805b7d8/Packs/IntSight/Integrations/Rapid7ThreatCommand/README.md","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0002.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8954696320cbff8f7d95f98854cf0e72222fc646/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-222m-mgc9-9mqv/GHSA-222m-mgc9-9mqv.json","https://github.com/MAECProject/python-maec/blob/13e66105c9646156060d0896a4d54970ea358f44/maec/bindings/maec_bundle.py","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/FIRSTdotorg/Vuln4Cast/blob/c93910d268aa5b5d2260adb9b5d92094b2d06daf/YearlyVuln4Cast-V1.ipynb"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0003.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1250","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1250.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1185","title":"SCO mscreen 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SCO OpenServer 及其他 SCO 操作系统中 mscreen 程序存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过在 .mscreenrc 配置文件中设置超长 TERM 环境变量条目，触发 mscreen 中的缓冲区溢出，从而劫持程序执行流程，获得 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SCO OpenServer Enterprise System、CMW、Open Desktop、Internet FastStart 等多个产品，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1185"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-10-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:54.020","remediation":"该漏洞影响已停止维护的 SCO OpenServer 5.0.x 系列，官方早已不再提供安全更新。建议立即升级至受支持的 Linux/Unix 发行版（如 RHEL、Ubuntu LTS）以彻底消除风险；若无法迁移，可移除 mscreen 的 setuid 位（`chmod u-s /usr/bin/mscreen`）并限制本地非授信用户登录作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90686250717719&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1379","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/261","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1185.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1185","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1185.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1185.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vj3r-fw7h-xqg9/GHSA-vj3r-fw7h-xqg9.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1185.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--bd961089-d6e4-4666-8665-7ba0d5099b99.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/NVDFeatureAnalysis/blob/493a57a415cc110f9945148abd717eeb92f6ca7e/originalDataset/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1250.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1250.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1250.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1457","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1457.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1291","title":"Microsoft Windows 95/NT 4.0 TCP/IP 实现远程TCP连接重置漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 95及Windows NT 4.0的TCP/IP协议栈实现存在安全漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过发送PSH ACK等特殊构造的数据包，强制目标重置连接并从响应包中获取目标的最后一个序列号，随后伪造RST数据包断开目标与对端的TCP连接，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响所有运行Windows 95和Windows NT 4.0的系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1291"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1998-10-05","updated":"2024-06-16","remediation":"Windows 95和Windows NT 4.0已停止支持，建议升级到受支持的Windows版本。若无法升级，在网络边界部署防火墙过滤异常TCP包并启用TCP序列号随机化机制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2024-06-01T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/10789","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1383"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1457.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0562","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0562.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0343","title":"The Palace 客户端远程代码执行漏洞","description":"The Palace 是一款图形化在线聊天软件，其客户端存在远程代码执行漏洞。恶意 Palace 服务器管理员可通过向连接的客户端发送特制的指令数据包，诱使客户端执行任意系统命令或程序。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，受害者仅需连接至受控服务器即可触发。该漏洞影响全部 Palace 客户端版本，可导致客户端被完全控制。目前该软件已停止维护，无官方补丁提供。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0343"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1998-10-02","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"The Palace 客户端软件已于 2000 年代初停止维护，官方未发布任何安全补丁。建议立即停用该软件，迁移至 Signal、Matrix 等仍在维护的即时通讯方案。如确需继续使用，务必在隔离沙箱环境中运行客户端，仅连接可信服务器，并以最小权限账户执行，避免连接不受控的 Palace 服务器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0343","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0343.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0343","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0343.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0fec8c5c64ee33c93da01ddd0b28bf8f9f743a61/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0343.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/3f4ce19e2c9952be92df5da9390e93383644298b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g4rh-vxc3-fpmr/GHSA-g4rh-vxc3-fpmr.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0343.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a